as inthe group that helped Groul get Innoruuk Curse this past week and fough with him quite a bit the following 24 hours.  That blade is incredible a 1500 pt DD/DOT proc.  Damn.  Then i look at staff of 4.  a componentless diamonskin basically.  call me a ingrate but i was hoping for something nicer.  <br>
<br>
I know i will probably never have one anyways but looking at how it works the melees are set with the procs thier weapons have.  the masters of DD kinda got hosed here.  the water sprinkler is cool just cause manaless rez's makes you a raids best friend.  Bards is nice for bards the +20% effect on all songs makes them cool all around.  <br>
<br>
I cannot comment on any of the others casters epics cause i havent even looked at them.  <br>
<br>
Just a couple questions.  Please dont take this cas class whining cause i play 8 different classes on brell and love them all they all have thier strong and weak points but the epics i just wish were more epic for all.  Give the casters a ability they didnt already have.  the procs on weapons give him a ability they normally dont have (at least to that degree).  mabe next year when they impliment the godly weapons (which they should do cause everyone will be bored of epics then and they will be far too common)<br>
<br>
 <p>Vinar Ruinthang<BR>
