ph33r m3
/em waddles off looking l33t</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=oakendar>Oakendar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.geocities.com/researchtriangle/6999/yang.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 236<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/8/01 9:08:36 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   umm.</span><hr size=1> Umm I think the Wizzy buffs just add the capacity for health, not the health itself.  Everytime I see one cast it on themeselves their hp bar goes down.  If this is the case, Diamondskin would not heal damage already taken.<br>
<br>
